v1.1 incorporates mandatory amendments following independent review dated 12 April 2026. Changes address: enforcement protocol (new Section 11), engineering integration requirements (new Section 12), measurable criteria added to all eight principles, revision of Section 3A from absolute ban to conditional guidance, removal of the 'AI-generated sameness' anti-pattern, addition of accessibility and mobile scope requirements. A full change log appears at Appendix B. Sections commended by the review (Founding Principle, Sections 2, 4, 5) remain intact.



